  <section class="os-why" aria-labelledby="why-title"><div class="shell"><p class="os-eyebrow">WHY BOMSOCIETY</p><h2 id="why-title">Decision guidance built for the Business of Medicine.</h2><p>Not a course. Not a blog. Each Decision Episode turns a consequential question into a clear next move—at the pace and depth a physician needs.</p><a class="os-text-link" href="{{@site.url}}/about/">See the physician-first approach <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></div></section>

  <section class="os-living" aria-labelledby="living-title"><div class="shell"><div class="os-section-heading"><div><p class="os-eyebrow">A LIVING PRODUCT</p><h2 id="living-title">Useful now. Improving with every protected decision.</h2></div><p>Editorially featured while the library grows.</p></div><div class="os-living-grid"><article><b>EDITOR'S FEATURED DECISION</b><h3>Compensation formulas</h3><p>Understand what to request before you assess an offer.</p><a href="#compensation-pathway">Start the framework →</a></article><article><b>WHAT PHYSICIANS ARE ASKING</b><h3>What should I clarify before I sign?</h3><p>Employment Contracts is being built around the questions that matter most.</p><button type="button" data-library-decision="Employment Contracts" data-availability="coming_next">Add your question →</button></article><article><b>UPCOMING DECISION EPISODE</b><h3>AI in Practice</h3><p>A practical framework for evaluating adoption, oversight, and value.</p><button type="button" data-library-decision="Artificial Intelligence" data-availability="coming_next">Preview the framework →</button></article></div><a class="os-text-link" href="#decision-library">See every Decision Episode <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></div></section>

