  <section class="os-first-win" aria-labelledby="first-win-title" data-track-section="first_decision_win"><div class="shell os-first-win-grid"><div><p class="os-eyebrow">A USEFUL START · 30 SECONDS</p><h2 id="first-win-title">A compensation number is not a compensation formula.</h2><p>Before you weigh an offer, ask for the written formula, its threshold, and two recent reconciliation statements.</p></div><div class="os-first-win-action"><span aria-hidden="true">01</span><strong>One request can change the whole conversation.</strong><button type="button" class="os-text-link" data-library-decision="Compensation" data-availability="available">Use this framework <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></button></div></div></section>

